CHAPTER 10 : RAID LEVELS

What is RAID, Types of RAID`s, RAID Levels (RAID0, RAID1,RAID10, RAID5)

RAID (Redundant Array of Independent Disk)

RAID0, 
RAID1,
RAID10, 
RAID5
